    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It runs and drives flawlessly, with no mechanical issues. The exterior is essentially free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the interior shows no signs of wear. All systems function as intended, and the vehicle has been exceptionally well maintained.",
      "price": 46500.0,
